headline.main: 2 TINY SUBMARINES RAISED AT SYDNEY; Midget Raiders Sank Barracks Ship Before Going Down -- 19 Are Dead or Missing

lead_paragraph: MELBOURNE, Australia, Tuesday, June 2 -- Two of the three midget Japanese submarines sunk by gunfire and depth charges when they raided Sydney's harbor Sunday night have been raised from the bottom of the harbor.
abstract: 2 of 3 Jap submarines sunk in raid on Sydney harbor raised
